’Щ@9a2078604f59f57fa7925da440e34ba1f7c25366ba6b43c434d2989d70a24df4ЩёTitle: title: debug
Path: Flags
Content:
``--raw, -r``
: Prints the raw value representation.
``--raw-value, -v``
: Prints the raw value representation but not the nushell value part.
